name: Protector (Enstrn)
description:
The game is about the Astranout(Astranaut) who needs to get to the Spaceship and is helped by the Ninja which is armed.  On the way are some tricky obstactles and some tanks. 

Developed for the global game jam Nepal 2022.

Controls => A , D for movement  ,  Space for jump , Left Control for character change and left mouse click for attack.

Developer:

Sweekar Mani Khadka(E Hakel)

Random dude on the internet for some assets.
